- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a possible category as the paper discusses the potential impact of blockchain technology on financial and other institutions. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper discusses the implementation of blockchain protocols. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper discusses the challenges and open questions in the development of quantum and hybrid quantum-classical blockchain protocols.
